item.title: Spd1.5 final blog post
item.description: What is Snag a File? Snag a file is a product in active development that allows users to make use of all of that bandwidth they pay for when downloading files or content off the internet Why? As someone who pays for expensive internet, I’d like to actually make use of what i’m paying for. Plus time is a resource and we often can be stuck downloading files for hours so I built Snag a file, a utility that makes use of Goâ€™s concurrency features.
